{"snp5.5:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 5.5 ","snp5.5:0.2":"Mettagumanavapuccha ","snp5.5:1.1":"“Pucchami tam bhagava bruhi me tam, ","snp5.5:1.2":"(iccayasma mettagu) ","snp5.5:1.3":"Mannami tam vedagum bhavitattam; ","snp5.5:1.4":"Kuto nu dukkha samudagata ime, ","snp5.5:1.5":"Ye keci lokasmimanekarupa”. ","snp5.5:2.1":"“Dukkhassa ve mam pabhavam apucchasi, ","snp5.5:2.2":"(mettaguti bhagava) ","snp5.5:2.3":"Tam te pavakkhami yatha pajanam; ","snp5.5:2.4":"Upadhinidana pabhavanti dukkha, ","snp5.5:2.5":"Ye keci lokasmimanekarupa. ","snp5.5:3.1":"Yo ve avidva upadhim karoti, ","snp5.5:3.2":"Punappunam dukkhamupeti mando; ","snp5.5:3.3":"Tasma pajanam upadhim na kayira, ","snp5.5:3.4":"Dukkhassa jatippabhavanupassi”. ","snp5.5:4.1":"“Yam tam apucchimha akittayi no, ","snp5.5:4.2":"Annam tam pucchama tadingha bruhi; ","snp5.5:4.3":"Katham nu dhira vitaranti ogham, ","snp5.5:4.4":"Jatim jaram sokapariddavanca; ","snp5.5:4.5":"Tam me muni sadhu viyakarohi, ","snp5.5:4.6":"Tatha hi te vidito esa dhammo”. ","snp5.5:5.1":"“Kittayissami te dhammam, ","snp5.5:5.2":"(mettaguti bhagava) ","snp5.5:5.3":"Ditthe dhamme anitiham; ","snp5.5:5.4":"Yam viditva sato caram, ","snp5.5:5.5":"Tare loke visattikam”. ","snp5.5:6.1":"“Tancaham abhinandami, ","snp5.5:6.2":"mahesi dhammamuttamam; ","snp5.5:6.3":"Yam viditva sato caram, ","snp5.5:6.4":"tare loke visattikam”. ","snp5.5:7.1":"“Yam kinci sampajanasi, ","snp5.5:7.2":"(mettaguti bhagava) ","snp5.5:7.3":"Uddham adho tiriyancapi majjhe; ","snp5.5:7.4":"Etesu nandinca nivesananca, ","snp5.5:7.5":"Panujja vinnanam bhave na titthe. ","snp5.5:8.1":"Evamvihari sato appamatto, ","snp5.5:8.2":"Bhikkhu caram hitva mamayitani; ","snp5.5:8.3":"Jatim jaram sokapariddavanca, ","snp5.5:8.4":"Idheva vidva pajaheyya dukkham”. ","snp5.5:9.1":"“Etabhinandami vaco mahesino, ","snp5.5:9.2":"Sukittitam gotamanupadhikam; ","snp5.5:9.3":"Addha hi bhagava pahasi dukkham, ","snp5.5:9.4":"Tatha hi te vidito esa dhammo. ","snp5.5:10.1":"Te capi nunappajaheyyu dukkham, ","snp5.5:10.2":"Ye tvam muni atthitam ovadeyya; ","snp5.5:10.3":"Tam tam namassami samecca naga, ","snp5.5:10.4":"Appeva mam bhagava atthitam ovadeyya”. ","snp5.5:11.1":"“Yam brahmanam vedagumabhijanna, ","snp5.5:11.2":"Akincanam kamabhave asattam; ","snp5.5:11.3":"Addha hi so oghamimam atari, ","snp5.5:11.4":"Tinno ca param akhilo akankho. ","snp5.5:12.1":"Vidva ca yo vedagu naro idha, ","snp5.5:12.2":"Bhavabhave sangamimam visajja; ","snp5.5:12.3":"So vitatanho anigho niraso, ","snp5.5:12.4":"Atari so jatijaranti brumi”ti. ","snp5.5:12.5":"Mettagumanavapuccha catutthi. "}